[Amit Varma]: His book is called The Great Repression and is basically an excellent book of history

00:02:07.840 --> 00:02:13.600
[Amit Varma]: that places the framing of laws in the context of the political and social environments in

00:02:13.600 --> 00:02:19.040
[Amit Varma]: which they were born, an extremely insightful book with many TIL moments.

