00:44:09.920 --> 00:44:14.000
[Amit Varma]: You had the Normans and the Saxons and the Celts and all of that sort of fighting for

00:44:14.000 --> 00:44:18.760
[Amit Varma]: dominance and therefore for the centralizing authority that cropped up in the shape of

00:44:18.760 --> 00:44:23.760
[Amit Varma]: the king and especially Edward the first who was like you point out of a legislative bent.

00:44:23.760 --> 00:44:29.000
[Amit Varma]: There was an importance to have laws which would keep these people in check.

