00:47:54.120 --> 00:48:00.160
[Amit Varma]: And let's let's get back to the subject at hand, which is so there is this law which

00:48:00.160 --> 00:48:02.520
[Amit Varma]: aims to protect.

00:48:02.520 --> 00:48:06.640
[Amit Varma]: You've also pointed out the distinction between two kinds of laws, which is that there are

00:48:06.640 --> 00:48:10.720
[Amit Varma]: laws which protect you from other citizens, which are meant to stop citizens harming other

00:48:10.720 --> 00:48:11.720
[Amit Varma]: citizens.

00:48:11.720 --> 00:48:13.640
[Amit Varma]: And there are laws which are meant to protect the state.

00:48:13.640 --> 00:48:14.640
[Amit Varma]: Yes.

00:48:14.640 --> 00:48:17.880
[Amit Varma]: And and this is sort of in the category of that.

