00:50:24.880 --> 00:50:29.760
[Guest]: So yeah, so 1857, as you know, was the, they called it the first war of independence, but

00:50:29.760 --> 00:50:34.920
[Guest]: it was more an organized mutiny across the country.

00:50:34.920 --> 00:50:38.400
[Guest]: So and it again was on mostly on religious grounds.

